TITLE: Episode 104 - A Menagerie of Monsters with the Cryptid Bartender [Adult Language]
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by the illustrious Harley from Cryptid Bartender. We will be chopping it up about jackalopes, Jersey Devils, Nessie, and Bigfeet and touching on the interest in the mythical. Join us for a great time.
